headline.main: Dutch Nationalist Wilders-Ban Turkish Campaigning in the Netherlands
headline.print_headline: Dutch Nationalist Wilders-Ban Turkish Campaigning in the Netherlands

lead_paragraph: Dutch nationalist Geert Wilders, who is expected to make huge gains in a March 15 election, said on Sunday he would ban Turkish officials from political campaigning in the Netherlands.
